{"tid":450227,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［自家制］無花果鮮奶撻","createTime":"2017-10-28T03:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T03:45:24.000Z","uid":46234,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"548cc36b15dcfc2435d279fe228e912c0a99a1af","tid":450227,"uid":46234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/113211_0e3ccf8127c53d8f4bb3a7bdf8ef39c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F113211_0e3ccf8127c53d8f4bb3a7bdf8ef39c7.jpg&h=6f1152c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/113212_ae4283ecb8116b0934e5baaa7c003672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F113212_ae4283ecb8116b0934e5baaa7c003672.jpg&h=14551cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食譜：<br />\n麵粉 75g<br />\n牛油 40g<br />\n糖 2湯匙（分開1.5同0.5湯匙）<br />\n鮮奶 70g <br />\n雞蛋 1隻 （雞蛋分一小匙份量作撻皮用）<br />\n無花果一隻<br />\n<br />\n準備工作：預熱焗爐180度<br />\n                    切無花果<br />\n<br />\n1. 先將牛油、麵粉和糖（1.5匙）用手搓至雜碎狀<br />\n2. 加入一小匙蛋漿至麵團（太濕加小小麵粉）<br />\n3.  將撻模掃油，將麵團平均灘在撻模<br />\n4. 用叉吉撻底數次，入焗爐20分鐘<br />\n5. 取出撻底後，將切好的無花果放靚靚，將剩下材料攪拌均勻過篩倒進撻模，再焗10分鐘，完成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS. 可以將無花果轉其他生果"}]}